cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CE, cs.SI, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a novel approach to personalization algorithms using artificial intelligence concepts, specifically reinforcement learning. This falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence, which is covered by cs.AI and cs.LG. The application of this approach to the inverse problem of cardiac electrophysiology and whole-body circulation model suggests that it could also fall under the categories of computational engineering (cs.CE) and systems and control (cs.SI). Finally, the use of reinforcement learning as the underlying concept also suggests that it could fall under the category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
